author: By MICHELLE R. SMITH and DEE-ANN DURBIN Associated Press
title: Many businesses cautious about restarting economy amid virus
description: PROVIDENCE, R.I. (AP) — President Donald Trump wants the country open for business by mid-April, but some experts warn it's not as easy as flipping a switch: Economies run on confidence, and that is likely to be in short supply…
